435
00:42:36,764 --> 00:42:38,348
Merda...

436
00:42:41,310 --> 00:42:42,561
Nossa!

437
00:42:45,856 --> 00:42:47,024
Sam.

438
00:42:47,691 --> 00:42:49,193
